children.description: Given that David goes to the web
David opens the browser on Google Home Page
David opens the Computrabajo home page
Then the search field
When he clicks the registry button
David clicks on register option

And tries to register with his old information
| Name | Lastnames | Email | Password | Desired Job | Department |
| David | Ayala Gomez |  | olakase123 | Ingeniero | Antioquia |
David enters 'David' into name input text
David enters 'Ayala Gomez' into lastnames input text
David enters '' into email input text
David enters 'olakase123' into password input text
David enters 'Ingeniero' into desired position input text
David clicks on department dropdown list
David clicks on button to continue with the registry
Then he should see the message "Obligatorio"
Then the error message should be 'Obligatorio'
